mods.abstract: Two color window card (black and red on white) Hatching poster announcing in person Faron Young and the Deputies show with Martha Carson and Little Jimmy Dickens and the Country Boys at Oneida High School Auditorium. Poster features metal photoplate of Faron Young, Martha Carson, and Little Jimmy Dickens.
